title: Ask Charlie Anything 125: Could New York Go Red? Biden's Barbie Pocket Moment? Missouri Firefighter Executed? and MORE
itunes:title: Ask Charlie Anything 125: Could New York Go Red? Biden's Barbie Pocket Moment? Missouri Firefighter Executed? and MORE
description:
Charlie takes the questions you email him at Freedom@CharlieKirk.com including:

Is it actually possible that New York would go Republican? Does Lee Zeldin stand a chance? Why are parents so in support of the GOP? Why did a good Samaritan firefighter get executed in Missouri and no charges were filed? Why is Joe Biden meeting with the TikToker behind "Girlhood," who presents a misogynistic parody of what he thinks a woman is like, and give Biden an opportunity to GOTV with the trans community. Stacey Abrams believes that abortion is super important and why? 

Support the show: http://www.charliekirk.com/support
